43:29.774 --> 43:34.188
When I was 5 years old, that woman
told me I could breathe underwater.

43:34.362 --> 43:36.398
My little ass almost drowned.

43:36.572 --> 43:41.532
So, no, boyfriend, I don't listen
to most of what come out her mouth.

43:41.702 --> 43:43.533
She's schizophrenic...

43:43.704 --> 43:46.662
...but it doesn't mean
that she's not perceptive.

43:47.500 --> 43:50.242
Look, just let me say this,
then I'll get off your back, all right?

43:50.419 --> 43:51.750
LAFAYETTE:
Mm-hm.

43:52.171 --> 43:56.130
Dealing drugs is very dangerous
for somebody like you.

43:56.717 --> 44:00.460
All that energy you've got,
it can go dark if you let it.

44:00.638 --> 44:03.550
I think you've been hanging around
my mama too long.

44:03.724 --> 44:06.557
Her crazy is starting to rub off on you.

44:08.729 --> 44:11.971
-|'|| be back in the morning to pick her up.
-Jesus, wait.

44:15.695 --> 44:19.279
The dealing, I ain't got no choice. I don't.

44:19.448 --> 44:22.235
I've been trying to stop for a while now.
It's not that easy.

44:24.245 --> 44:27.282
And if you don't want nothing
to do with me, that's fine.

44:27.456 --> 44:31.074
| just wanted to let you know because--

44:40.803 --> 44:42.964
[BETO VILLARES' "NACAO POSTAL"
PLAYING OVER SPEAKERS]

44:55.610 --> 44:57.316
Checkmate.

45:00.239 --> 45:01.900
I'm bored.

45:02.074 --> 45:03.154
Take off your clothes.

45:06.495 --> 45:09.111
A little privacy?

45:10.333 --> 45:12.039
Everybody out.

45:12.210 --> 45:13.541
[HISSES]

45:37.485 --> 45:38.816
[HISSES]

45:39.362 --> 45:41.523
It's been a long time since I've done this.

45:41.697 --> 45:45.315
-A man?
-No, a vampire.

45:47.119 --> 45:48.825
[BOTH GROWLING]

46:07.515 --> 46:09.471
Anybody here?

46:11.519 --> 46:13.180
Hello?

46:13.771 --> 46:15.056
[DOOR SLAMS]

46:15.231 --> 46:17.187
[IRON HORSE'S "NIGHT ON THE SUN"
PLAYING ON RADIO]

46:30.496 --> 46:32.737
Hey! Is anybody in--?

46:32.915 --> 46:34.906
[FLIES BUZZING]

46:56.188 --> 46:57.519
[MAN GROANS]

47:01.652 --> 47:03.643
[MAN SLURPING AND GROWLING]

47:07.616 --> 47:08.651
[HISSES]

47:08.826 --> 47:10.862
Fuck.

47:17.793 --> 47:20.330
-Who in the hell are you?
JASON: You Crystal's father?

47:20.504 --> 47:23.587
-Wait, you're the guy from the--
-I'm the guy holding the gun.

47:23.758 --> 47:27.250
And I'm telling you
Crystal ain't never coming back here.

47:27.428 --> 47:31.797
-And you ain't never going near her again.
-Stupid punk.

47:31.974 --> 47:36.388
-You got no idea who you're messing with.
-No, you got no idea.

47:36.562 --> 47:40.521
I'm a cop, and I know what you're up to.

47:40.691 --> 47:44.604
So you're gonna leave Crystal
the fuck alone.

47:45.738 --> 47:49.822
Or me and the whole sheriff's department
gonna come after you...

47:49.992 --> 47:53.075
...and your hillbilly freak show.

47:53.412 --> 47:54.948
You feel me?

47:55.915 --> 47:57.906
[DOOR SLAMS AND ENGINE STARTS]

48:02.588 --> 48:06.206
Oh, yeah. I feel you, boy.

48:19.730 --> 48:21.391
[DOG HOWLS AND SOOKIE GASPS]

48:24.318 --> 48:26.309
[DOGS HOWLING]

48:39.166 --> 48:40.497
[CHUCKLES]

48:50.177 --> 48:51.553
[BILL HISSES]

48:51.720 --> 48:53.711
[GROWLING]

48:54.181 --> 48:55.170
[GROWLING]

48:56.600 --> 48:58.591
[BILL & WEREWOLF GROWLING
AND GRUNTING]

49:05.025 --> 49:06.561
Hi.

49:06.735 --> 49:08.191
[HISSES]

49:08.904 --> 49:10.815
[WEREWOLF SQUEALING]

49:14.952 --> 49:16.408
[GRUNTING]

49:18.497 --> 49:20.203
DEBBIE:
Open up, little piggy.

49:21.125 --> 49:24.868
Or I'll huff and I'll puff...

49:25.045 --> 49:28.037
...and I'll blow your house down.

49:28.215 --> 49:30.206
I don't wanna kill you, but I will.

49:31.802 --> 49:34.794
I got nothing left to live for anyway.

49:34.972 --> 49:36.007
[CHUCKLES]

49:36.182 --> 49:37.763
You took it all.

49:37.933 --> 49:41.050
You brought this on yourself, Debbie.

49:41.228 --> 49:43.310
Take another step and I will shoot.

49:43.481 --> 49:46.063
Why don't you just pull the trigger now?

49:46.233 --> 49:47.222
What do you care?

49:47.401 --> 49:51.440
There's people that still love you for reasons
I ain't even gonna try to make sense of.

49:51.864 --> 49:53.570
Wow.

49:53.741 --> 49:56.073
Talking to me about love.

49:56.243 --> 49:59.656
How noble and shit. Bitch, please.

50:00.080 --> 50:02.571
I see right through you.

50:03.792 --> 50:08.252
You fuck vampires and werewolves
because your own kind rejects you.

50:09.548 --> 50:12.415
They know you're nothing but a freak.

50:14.470 --> 50:18.304
I've had vampire blood. Lots of it.

50:18.474 --> 50:20.465
Me too.

50:20.643 --> 50:22.099
Your boyfriend's yummy.

50:31.445 --> 50:32.651
[LAUGHS]

50:35.991 --> 50:37.982
[GROWLING]

50:38.452 --> 50:40.443
[SOOKIE & DEBBIE YELLING
AND GRUNTING]

50:42.581 --> 50:45.448
JESSICA: Hey. Get back here.
-Jessica, stay in the house!

50:45.626 --> 50:46.661
[JESSICA SCREAMS]

50:46.835 --> 50:48.120
[CLATTERING]

50:51.298 --> 50:55.257
Since no one was hospitable enough to
invite me in, I had to wait till you came out.

50:55.427 --> 50:58.510
JESSICA: Help.
-I take it this is yours.

50:58.681 --> 50:59.841
Let her go.

51:00.975 --> 51:03.842
What do you think, Gus?
Should I let her go?

51:04.728 --> 51:05.808
[BARKING]

51:05.980 --> 51:09.939
Oh. Well, I take it that's a no.
I'll tell you what.

51:10.109 --> 51:14.819
I'll trade you the red one
for the blond one.

51:15.489 --> 51:17.525
How about you and I settle this
among men?

51:17.700 --> 51:19.691
Aw. How very sexist of you, Bill.

51:19.868 --> 51:23.156
When it comes to killing,
I have always been an equal opportunist.

51:23.330 --> 51:25.321
[SCREAMING]

51:26.458 --> 51:28.449
You are 3000 years old and a king...

51:28.627 --> 51:32.336
...yet you hide behind guards, wolves...

51:32.923 --> 51:35.380
...a baby vampire.

51:35.551 --> 51:37.507
Are you a coward...

51:39.013 --> 51:41.004
...or are you just lazy?

51:41.181 --> 51:43.172
[LAUGHING]

51:44.184 --> 51:45.799
Here you go, boy.

51:45.978 --> 51:47.889
-Rip her to shreds.
JESSICA: No.

51:52.401 --> 51:54.392
[WEREWOLF SNARLING]

51:57.156 --> 52:00.740
Northman was right about you.
You are a waste of the blood.

52:01.160 --> 52:03.151
[BILL YELLING]

52:10.127 --> 52:14.871
Silver spurs. You like?

52:15.049 --> 52:17.290
[GRUNTING]

52:26.894 --> 52:28.384
DEBBIE:
Fuck!

52:47.665 --> 52:49.280
Fuck!

52:56.882 --> 52:59.214
[DEBBIE SCREAMS AND SOBS]

53:20.280 --> 53:23.647
-Turn over.
-Oh, yes, Daddy.

53:27.287 --> 53:29.278
[TALBOT SIGHING]

53:32.626 --> 53:34.537
ERIC:
Russell took my family.

53:35.921 --> 53:38.003
-Now I take his.
-No!

53:38.173 --> 53:40.164
[ERIC YELLS AND TALBOT SCREAMS]

53:42.136 --> 53:43.171
Talbot.

53:46.223 --> 53:47.383
Yes.

53:47.558 --> 53:51.346
No!

53:54.982 --> 53:57.223
Get out of my house, bitch!

53:57.651 --> 53:59.152
Fuck you.

54:01.238 --> 54:03.854
Next time I won't miss.

54:21.675 --> 54:23.336
SooMe.

54:29.183 --> 54:31.265
-I love you.
-I'm sorry.

54:31.435 --> 54:33.517
SOOKIE: I love you.
-I'm sorry.

54:35.147 --> 54:37.103
I'm so sorry.

54:37.274 --> 54:39.640
-I love you.
-I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

54:39.818 --> 54:41.479
SOOKIE:
I love you.

54:48.577 --> 54:50.568
[OTEP'S "HEAD" PLAYING ON RADIO]

54:53.499 --> 54:54.705
[SOBS]

55:03.008 --> 55:04.999
[MAN SCREAMING]

55:07.763 --> 55:09.344
[JESSICA MOANING]

55:09.515 --> 55:12.723
I'm sorry. Please don't kill me.
I don't wanna die.

55:15.270 --> 55:17.261
[SCREAMS]

55:31.036 --> 55:33.027
[SOOKIE MOANING]

55:39.378 --> 55:41.369
[BILL MOANING]

55:59.898 --> 56:00.933
[BILL YELLS]
